sourceMeaningMnemonic: Dig up a <radical>mole</radical> and you <kanji>attain</kanji> a mole status. You're always trying to attain a new level for yourself and now you get to be on the mole level!
meaningInfo: It's actually pretty easy to attain mole status. Just stand in a field. Wait for the ground to move under you and shove your hand in the earth. Blam! An achievement pops up above your head and you're there.
readingMnemonic: Mole isn't enough, you want to <kanji>attain</kanji> <reading>shee</reading>p (<ja>し</ja>) status next. Everyone knows it goes human > mole> sheep. Now you need to stand in the field with the mole and get a sheep to come over.
readingInfo: If you can attain two animal levels in one day you'll be a legend on the leaderboards.
